cards.helptext:
Material

The basic material or medium of which the Resource is composed, eg. Ceramic, Plastic, Brick. The material can be further qualified by the addition of a Material Name

Material Name

Use this field to record the name commonly used for a particular, or characteristic, material. This may be the vernacular or generally used name for a certain type of material or a brand name eg. Samian ware, Bakelite, Teflon.

Material Type

Use this field to record the how the material has been used.

cards.description:
Generic branch for capturing free-form written descriptive information.
Intended to be evolution from v3 description branch from HIP 3. Created semantic description node with description string and description type hanging off of it. Description (semantic node) becomes a grouping node (type and string).  

This branch meets technical business rules for CRM compliance but CRM experts have said that this is an inappropriate implementation of E62.

Connects to all resources with P140i
